articles.title: Third Roland Garros win sets Iga Swiatek on the path to greatness - The Guardian
articles.description: Each of the Pole’s wins at the French Open have shown different dimensions and developments within her game
articles.content: In the days leading up to the 2020 French Open, Iga Swiatek was struggling through one of the biggest crises of her career. Having started the Covid-delayed autumn clay-court season with lofty hopes … [+9370 chars]
